sentences: The band emerged in 2014 with the song "Lhůta záruční".
Barbora Zelená, the finalist of the Miss 2011 competition, appeared in the video for their second song "Celibát".
In 2015 they released their debut album Katarze.
The album sold 3,000 copies in its first week and entered the Czech charts at number one, and was certified platinum after three weeks.
